zipkin.storage

Interface AsyncSpanStore


  • public interface AsyncSpanStore
    An interface that is equivalent to SpanStore but accepts callbacks to allow bridging to async libraries.

    Note: This is not considered a user-level Api, rather an Spi that can be used to bind user-level abstractions such as futures or observables.

    See Also:
